msgid ""
"Password are scored in three levels: ``Strong``, ``Acceptable``, "
"``Insecure``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../security/ApplicationSecurity.rst:55
msgid ""
"Strong: A strong password should be formed by capital letters, lowercase "
"letters, numbers and a symbols, be at least 12 characters long and "
"include a variety of at least 10 different inputs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../security/ApplicationSecurity.rst:56
msgid ""
"Acceptable: An acceptable password should be formed by at least 3 "
"different inputs over capital letters, lowercase letters, numbers and a "
"symbols, be at least 10 characters and include a variety of at least 7 "
"different inputs."
