msgid "Two Factor Authentication"
msgstr ""

#: ../../security/ApplicationSecurity.rst:63
msgid ""
"The system implements Two Factor Authentication (2FA) based on ``TOTP`` "
"based on `RFC 6238 <https://tools.ietf.org/rfc/rfc6238.txt>`_ algorithm "
"and 160 bits secrets."
msgstr ""

#: ../../security/ApplicationSecurity.rst:65
msgid ""
"Users are enabled to enroll for 2FA via their own preferences and "
"administrators can optionally enforce this requirement."
