msgid "TLS for SMTP Notification"
msgstr ""

#: ../../security/ApplicationSecurity.rst:410
msgid ""
"All of the notifications are sent through SMTP over TLS encrypted channel"
" by using SMTP/TLS or SMTPS, depending on the configuration."
msgstr ""

